					<box></box>
					<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
						<font size="11"/>
					</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[        I request you to make necessary adjustment in your account through Journal by debiting the Account Code “610102 – Transfer from Board – Receipt adjusted” and credit to the funds accounts of the scheme concerned in the monthly account at once.  "]]></text>
